Localization.Name: Rust (Bottle)
Localization.Description:
HEI: 07
Effects: Cognitive Impairment, Dehydrating

Rumored to be so potent that it can be used to strip rust off ship components, those who regularly drink this harsh, strong-tasting alcohol swear by it, claiming everything else tastes weak by comparison.
